No data quality issues found. All fields are populated and consistent.

C0 aggregation diagnostics
C0 collapses C1 measure names into act-level clusters. The three scopes test different properties of that aggregation.

Per-document: granular aggregation symmetry
Per document, Figure 5 shows the compression ratio — how many surfaced measures collapse into each distinct act — by year and language. A symmetric aggregator should compress comparably on both sides; the previous clusterer fragmented BM more than EN.


Show code
