} else {
  pd0 &lt;- plot_malay_c0_perdoc(m$per_doc)
  if (is.null(pd0)) cat("No per-document aggregation available yet.\n") else print(pd0)
}





Figure 5: C0 per-document compression (measures collapsed into distinct acts) by year and language. Comparable EN/BM bars indicate symmetric aggregation.










